OL,3,CChildren under eight should not have
OL,4,Cslushie drinks with glycerol, experts
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FIt comes as a study highlighted a
OL,8,Fnumber of young people becoming unwell
OL,9,Fas a result of so-called "glycerol
OL,10,Fintoxication syndrome", which caused
OL,11,Fsymptoms like decreased consciousness
OL,12,Fand low blood sugar.
OL,14,FGlycerol is a naturally occurring
OL,15,Falcohol and sugar substitute which
OL,16,Fhelps slush drinks maintain their
OL,17,Ftexture by preventing liquid from
OL,18,Ffreezing solid.
