OL,7,FIn the UK, slush drinks ` also known
OL,8,Fas slushies ` containing the
OL,9,Fingredient are not recommended for
OL,10,Fchildren under the age of four.
OL,12,FHowever, academics have called for the
OL,13,Fpublic health advice to be revisited.
OL,15,FFor the review, published in Archives
OL,16,Fof Disease in Childhood, researchers
OL,17,Fat University College Dublin looked at
OL,18,Fthe medical notes of 21 children in
OL,19,Fthe UK and Ireland who fell ill after
OL,20,Fconsuming a slushie.
