OL,7,FMost cases took place between 2018 and
OL,8,F2024, with children's ages ranging
OL,9,Fbetween two and almost seven.
OL,11,FThe youngsters were initially
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with hypoglycaemia, or low
OL,13,Fblood sugar, after arriving at
OL,14,Femergency departments.
OL,16,FResearchers suggest drinking slushies
OL,17,Fcontaining glycerol "may cause a
OL,18,Fclinical syndrome of glycerol
OL,19,Fintoxication in young children".
